## OpenSearch Analytics Dashboard
Full-stack web dashboard for real-time log analysis and anomaly detection, built with Next.js, FastAPI, and PostgreSQL, deployed on AWS ECS.
**Demonstrates:** React, Next.js, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, AWS ECS, OpenSearch, Elasticsearch, full-stack development, data visualisation, anomaly detection
**Relevant for:** full-stack engineer, backend engineer, data engineer, SRE roles

## LLM-Powered Code Review Bot
GitHub Actions bot using GPT-4 to automatically review pull requests for security vulnerabilities and code quality issues.
**Demonstrates:** LLM integration, GPT-4, GitHub Actions, CI/CD, Python, developer tooling, prompt engineering, automation
**Relevant for:** AI/ML engineer, developer tools, backend engineer, DevOps roles

## Distributed Task Queue
Redis-backed distributed task queue built in Go supporting 10K concurrent workers with dead-letter queue and retry logic.
**Demonstrates:** Go, Redis, distributed systems, concurrency, message queuing, reliability engineering, systems programming
**Relevant for:** backend engineer, platform engineer, systems engineer, SRE roles
